A few days ago, they brought
some furniture to the villa opposite.

1527
01:55:32,476 --> 01:55:33,637
Did you notice?

1528
01:55:34,433 --> 01:55:37,300
I think so,
but I don't see much from in here.

1529
01:55:38,016 --> 01:55:39,046
Ask her.

1530
01:55:47,100 --> 01:55:48,509
Claire?

1531
01:55:48,682 --> 01:55:51,137
Listen to what
this gentleman wants to say.

1532
01:55:52,267 --> 01:55:53,296
Yes.

1533
01:55:54,682 --> 01:55:56,092
And the day after,

1534
01:55:56,266 --> 01:55:59,513
other workmen came
and took everything away again.

1535
01:56:01,641 --> 01:56:03,181
The day after?

1536
01:56:04,473 --> 01:56:08,419
In 18 months,
three deliveries and three removals.

1537
01:56:11,391 --> 01:56:13,676
I was here a while ago.

1538
01:56:14,973 --> 01:56:17,177
- Do you remember?
- Nine.

1539
01:56:19,639 --> 01:56:23,586
- What do you mean?
- You've been here nine times.

1540
01:56:25,640 --> 01:56:27,097
Today makes 10.

1541
01:56:27,431 --> 01:56:31,045
I was wondering if you saw
a woman leave the villa.

1542
01:56:32,304 --> 01:56:35,505
Medium height, light hair,
a bit pale?

1543
01:56:36,805 --> 01:56:40,669
- Yes.
- That time was 231.

1544
01:56:42,265 --> 01:56:43,721
Are you sure?

1545
01:56:44,055 --> 01:56:45,714
Then another six.

1546
01:56:46,556 --> 01:56:51,507
In a year and a half,
I saw her go out 237 times.

1547
01:56:51,887 --> 01:56:53,297
What did I say?

1548
01:56:53,471 --> 01:56:55,925
She's a phenomenon,
remembers everything.

1549
01:56:57,971 --> 01:56:59,512
It's not possible.

1550
01:57:02,053 --> 01:57:04,174
You were at the villa 63 times.

1551
01:57:04,513 --> 01:57:08,422
36 during the day and 27 at night,

1552
01:57:08,762 --> 01:57:11,085
excluding the night
of the accident.

1553
01:57:12,553 --> 01:57:15,966
- One, four, four.
- One, four, four?

1554
01:57:16,303 --> 01:57:18,543
The telephone number
for the ambulance.

1555
01:57:20,012 --> 01:57:21,588
The villa is free now.

1556
01:57:21,970 --> 01:57:24,886
If you're interested,
I'll get you a good deal.

1557
01:57:26,512 --> 01:57:29,129
- Who owns it?
- Me.

1558
01:57:30,344 --> 01:57:32,418
But I don't know what to do with it.

1559
01:57:33,510 --> 01:57:36,177
I often rent it out to cinema people.

1560
01:57:37,094 --> 01:57:38,468
Cinema people?

1561
01:57:39,053 --> 01:57:42,003
For the past two years,
it's been taken by the engineer

1562
01:57:42,178 --> 01:57:44,713
who does the lift
that takes me up to my house.

1563
01:57:45,510 --> 01:57:47,216
He's really nice, that boy.

1564
01:57:48,135 --> 01:57:49,793
He can do anything.

1565
01:57:49,968 --> 01:57:52,458
There's nothing he can't fix.

1566
01:57:53,051 --> 01:57:56,383
And he's always kissing me.

1567
01:57:56,551 --> 01:57:58,342
Bringing me flowers.

1568
02:00:43,668 --> 02:00:47,449
The Paris Express
is now arriving at platform seven.

1569
02:00:48,918 --> 02:00:50,624
Your attention, please.

1570
02:00:50,792 --> 02:00:53,625
The Berlin-Prague Arrow
is running 40 minutes late

1571
02:00:53,792 --> 02:00:54,989
due to fog on the line.

1572
02:00:56,835 --> 02:00:58,375
Come in, sir.

1573
02:00:59,709 --> 02:01:02,079
We furnished it
exactly as you requested.

1574
02:01:03,501 --> 02:01:05,989
And tomorrow, your trunks
will be delivered.

1575
02:01:06,167 --> 02:01:09,283
And later, I'll pass by
with a copy of your contract.

1576
02:01:09,626 --> 02:01:12,991
If there's anything else,
please don't hesitate to call.

1577
02:01:19,458 --> 02:01:20,999
Oh, Virgil.

1578
02:01:22,417 --> 02:01:26,623
If anything should happen to us,
I want you to know that I do love you.

1579
02:03:50,410 --> 02:03:52,483
Are you on your own, sir?

1580
02:04:03,117 --> 02:04:05,820
No. I'm waiting for someone.

